I own from my childhood.

3
00:02:35,975 --> 00:02:39,079
It was taken in 1955,
when I was 8 years old,

4
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:41,847
by my father
with a borrowed camera,

5
00:02:42,183 --> 00:02:44,384
and it's the only thing
I have left from those days...

6
00:02:44,385 --> 00:02:46,218
Except for my memories.

7
00:02:49,724 --> 00:02:51,424
This is a true story.

8
00:02:51,443 --> 00:02:53,543
This really happened to me.

9
00:02:59,618 --> 00:03:00,918
By 1962,

10
00:03:01,287 --> 00:03:02,854
I was 15 years old.

11
00:03:03,389 --> 00:03:05,023
I had 2 brothers and 3 sisters,

12
00:03:05,024 --> 00:03:06,657
no father, no money.

13
00:03:07,661 --> 00:03:09,095
I was the man of the house,

14
00:03:09,096 --> 00:03:10,863
and my mother, well...

15
00:03:11,699 --> 00:03:13,466
She was one of a kind.

16
00:03:25,247 --> 00:03:27,547
Christ!
You out of your mind?

17
00:03:27,683 --> 00:03:29,718
What's the matter
with you, asshole?

18
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:31,419
All right, all right.

19
00:03:33,323 --> 00:03:34,924
What's the matter with you?

20
00:03:34,925 --> 00:03:36,692
What's the matter with you?

21
00:03:36,693 --> 00:03:38,194
Mr. Owens to the
office immediately!

22
00:03:38,195 --> 00:03:39,495
Mist... aah!

23
00:03:41,498 --> 00:03:44,268
Fucking asshole!
You clean it up yourself!

24
00:03:44,269 --> 00:03:46,036
He's the one that started it!

25
00:03:46,037 --> 00:03:47,337
So did you!

26
00:03:47,438 --> 00:03:49,671
- Come on.
- Back off! Back off!

27
00:03:50,074 --> 00:03:51,574
He grabbed my ass!

28
00:03:51,643 --> 00:03:52,943
OK, come on!

29
00:04:06,393 --> 00:04:08,994
Oh, come on,
this wasn't my fault!

30
00:04:08,995 --> 00:04:10,362
Owens scared me!

31
00:04:11,399 --> 00:04:13,466
Look, I really need
this job, Mr. Nardin.

32
00:04:13,467 --> 00:04:15,268
You can't do this!
I got kids! Come on!

33
00:04:15,269 --> 00:04:16,569
You're fired.

34
00:04:16,770 --> 00:04:19,537
- I'm begging you, pl...
- you're fired!

35
00:04:40,197 --> 00:04:41,965
I told you,
I'm going to get money.

36
00:04:41,966 --> 00:04:43,499
I don't have the money now, OK.

37
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:45,368
You'll get the money later.

38
00:04:45,369 --> 00:04:46,735
I'll have all the money for you.

39
00:04:46,736 --> 00:04:48,103
Get off my back.

40
00:04:48,473 --> 00:04:50,373
Just lay off me on this,

41
00:04:50,541 --> 00:04:52,076
or you won't get nothing, OK?

42
00:04:52,077 --> 00:04:53,710
Just get off my back.

43
00:04:53,711 --> 00:04:55,679
I'm going to get
the money for you.

44
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,713
You'll get the money, man!

45
00:04:59,384 --> 00:05:00,684
Hi, kids.

46
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,820
