570
00:37:10,905 --> 00:37:12,205
Aah!

571
00:37:13,742 --> 00:37:15,042
Murray!

572
00:37:18,446 --> 00:37:19,746
Murray!

573
00:37:20,498 --> 00:37:21,798
Murray!

574
00:37:23,302 --> 00:37:24,836
Murray, you all right?

575
00:37:24,837 --> 00:37:26,137
