2 centimeters or so,

604
00:39:44,441 --> 00:39:46,108
and that nail would've
punctured his lung.

605
00:39:46,109 --> 00:39:47,744
- Is he ok?
- He's fine.

606
00:39:47,745 --> 00:39:48,745
Can I see him?

607
00:39:48,746 --> 00:39:49,879
You can take him home.

608
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,180
Oh!

609
00:39:52,083 --> 00:39:54,985
Just try to keep him in
bed for a couple of days

610
00:39:54,986 --> 00:39:57,019
