616
00:40:13,373 --> 00:40:15,206
I told her I'd keep it.

617
00:40:15,526 --> 00:40:16,959
But I wasn't dad,

618
00:40:17,027 --> 00:40:19,563
and I was sick of
pretending I was.

619
00:40:19,564 --> 00:40:21,165
I knew that when
the house was done,

620
00:40:21,166 --> 00:40:22,866
I was going back
to L.A.

621
00:40:22,867 --> 00:40:24,868
There was more to do,
I had friends there,

622
00:40:24,869 --> 00:40:26,769
and it was a lot warmer.

623
00:40:54,736 --> 00:40:55,702
Warm it up for you?

624
00:40:55,703 --> 00:40:57,003
Yes.

625
00:40:58,173 --> 00:41:02,073
And he says, "you're not
here for the hunt, are you?"

626
00:41:02,811 --> 00:41:04,345
Can I get you anything else?

627
00:41:04,346 --> 00:41:06,281
We're out of here, Franny.

628
00:41:06,282 --> 00:41:08,149
How about you and your
tribe helping us out

629
00:41:08,150 --> 00:41:10,317
over on that remodeling job?

630
00:41:11,087 --> 00:41:13,207
