635
00:41:21,932 --> 00:41:24,899
Dave, this means
more to me than money.

636
00:41:25,737 --> 00:41:27,037
Let's go.

637
00:41:33,077 --> 00:41:35,580
In Los Angeles,
mama worked her butt off

638
00:41:35,581 --> 00:41:37,948
just to get us from day to day.

639
00:41:38,117 --> 00:41:40,318
Now we all had to earn
enough to live on

640
00:41:40,319 --> 00:41:43,152
and put something away
for our house.

641
00:41:50,013 --> 00:41:53,082
We all worked on that house
every chance we got,

642
00:41:53,083 --> 00:41:55,218
but there were some things
we couldn't do,

643
00:41:55,219 --> 00:41:58,188
so mama hired contractors
for those jobs.

644
00:41:58,189 --> 00:41:59,489
God help 'em.

645
00:42:02,260 --> 00:42:03,560
Over here!

646
00:42:07,416 --> 00:42:09,684
Yeah, sure,
we can take care of it.

647
00:42:09,685 --> 00:42:11,052
I know you guys,

648
00:42:11,588 --> 00:42:14,056
you buy your goddamn
wiring and your fixtures,

649
00:42:14,057 --> 00:42:16,959
you mark it up 20, 50 percent,
and you soak me for it.

650
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:19,727
I want an estimate
for manpower only

651
00:42:19,796 --> 00:42:21,798
and a list of what
material you'll need.

652
00:42:21,799 --> 00:42:23,333
I'll haggle for
the materials myself.

653
00:42:23,334 --> 00:42:24,634
Any questions?

654
00:42:24,969 --> 00:42:26,369
I ain't got much time.

655
00:42:26,370 --> 00:42:28,203
I got to get to my job.

656
00:42:28,973 --> 00:42:30,674
I know you think
I'm a hard-nosed bitch.

657
00:42:30,675 --> 00:42:31,975
Don't deny it.

658
00:42:32,244 --> 00:42:34,078
I am when it comes
to this house.

659
00:42:34,079 --> 00:42:35,913
But I also know
I'm at your mercy.

660
00:42:35,914 --> 00:42:37,881
Treat me honestly
like I'll treat you.

661
00:42:37,882 --> 00:42:39,382
I'll deal in cash,

662
00:42:39,519 --> 00:42:41,453
so we may have to
do this piecemeal,

663
00:42:41,454 --> 00:42:43,655
but there won't be
any corner cutting.

664
00:42:43,656 --> 00:42:45,390
I want the best for this house.
The best.

665
00:42:45,391 --> 00:42:46,691
Lacey tribe.

666
00:42:59,241 --> 00:43:01,474
Show Mr. Whitman
your hands.

667
00:43:03,278 --> 00:43:05,078
Every penny you spend is a penny

668
00:43:05,079 --> 00:43:07,449
me and these
little hands earned.

669
00:43:07,450 --> 00:43:10,418
Don't make those blisters
count for nothing.

670
00:43:10,419 --> 00:43:14,119
There. I've tried it all...
guilt, fear, and pity.

671
00:43:14,390 --> 00:43:16,958
