00:43:33,277 --> 00:43:34,577
Yeah?

679
00:43:35,314 --> 00:43:37,414
Just what the hell is that?

680
00:43:37,683 --> 00:43:40,784
Well, my sister's red socks
got in with the whites,

681
00:43:40,785 --> 00:43:42,985
and it turned the sheets and
pillowcases and the t-shirt

682
00:43:43,009 --> 00:43:44,309
kind of pink.

683
