Go get another one.

684
00:43:45,925 --> 00:43:48,758
Well sir, this is
the only one I got.

685
00:43:48,961 --> 00:43:50,728
What, are you kidding?

686
00:43:51,531 --> 00:43:54,934
Lacey, I told you at the
beginning of the term

687
00:43:54,935 --> 00:43:56,969
