t-shirt, did I not?

688
00:43:56,970 --> 00:43:58,270
Yes, you did.

689
00:43:58,472 --> 00:44:00,172
White. Is that white?

690
00:44:01,108 --> 00:44:02,742
No, sir, it's a little off.

691
00:44:02,743 --> 00:44:04,043
A little off?

692
00:44:05,847 --> 00:44:08,614
I'd call that titty
pink, huh, guys?

693
00:44:09,183 --> 00:44:11,418
You're a shirt. You're a skin.
Let's go.

694
00:44:11,419 --> 00:44:12,988
Let's move it, guys.

695
00:44:12,989 --> 00:44:14,889
Let's go!
Lacey. Lacey.

696
00:44:19,195 --> 00:44:22,731
Listen, uh, why don't you just
go play with the girls?

697
00:44:22,732 --> 00:44:25,499
Better yet,
sit on the girls' bench.

698
00:44:28,305 --> 00:44:32,538
Your titty pink shirt will fit
in a lot better over there.

699
00:44:34,979 --> 00:44:37,946
Right over there
between the two girls.

700
00:44:43,422 --> 00:44:45,156
All right, guys, come on!

701
00:44:45,157 --> 00:44:47,024
Everybody over here.
Let's go!

702
00:44:47,025 --> 00:44:49,828
Shirts, you're going that way.
Skins, that way.

703
00:44:49,829 --> 00:44:51,929
Your grade depends on this.

704
00:45:06,580 --> 00:45:08,147
Her name was Raymi,

705
00:45:08,650 --> 00:45:10,551
and I couldn't have met her

706
00:45:10,552 --> 00:45:13,053
under more embarrassing
circumstances,

707
00:45:13,054 --> 00:45:17,021
