710
00:45:26,186 --> 00:45:28,219
I can read as good as you.

711
00:45:33,594 --> 00:45:35,996
Mom, Murray needs a compass
and protractor for school.

712
00:45:35,997 --> 00:45:37,630
Can't he borrow one?

713
00:45:37,933 --> 00:45:39,867
Mrs. Tipton said he has
to have a set of his own

714
00:45:39,868 --> 00:45:41,501
or she'll flunk him.

715
00:45:42,904 --> 00:45:45,005
I'll give you money
when you go back to school.

716
00:45:45,006 --> 00:45:46,306
Mama,

717
00:45:47,125 --> 00:45:48,625
I still feel sick.

718
00:45:50,045 --> 00:45:51,913
Just stay in bed, honey,
and keep warm.

719
00:45:51,914 --> 00:45:53,115
We'll save you something.

720
00:45:53,116 --> 00:45:54,416
Wait, Shayne!

721
00:45:56,886 --> 00:46:00,022
