722
00:46:00,023 --> 00:46:00,990
Damn, Shayne.
Another one?

723
00:46:00,991 --> 00:46:02,291
Yes.

724
00:46:03,260 --> 00:46:05,760
Take the potatoes and the gravy.

725
00:46:05,863 --> 00:46:07,430
Everybody sit down.

726
00:46:10,535 --> 00:46:13,235
You see, it's gotten
kind of green.

727
00:46:13,588 --> 00:46:16,790
Murray's green pants
got in with the whites.

728
00:46:16,791 --> 00:46:18,893
