What's the difference?

729
00:46:18,894 --> 00:46:20,928
What do you want, gold lami?

730
00:46:20,929 --> 00:46:22,962
Everybody else's is white.

731
00:46:23,500 --> 00:46:25,867
I got to have
a white t-shirt.

732
00:46:27,603 --> 00:46:30,570
Don't you tell me
what you got to have.

733
00:46:30,773 --> 00:46:33,543
You got to have a roof over your
head and food on the table,

734
00:46:33,544 --> 00:46:37,311
